      "blocks": {
        "philosophy-eyebrow": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>How we work</p>",
            "size": "sm",
            "uppercase": true,
            "muted": true
          }
        },
        "philosophy-heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "We consult first, cut second.",
            "size": "4xl"
          }
        },
        "philosophy-body": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Every appointment begins with a real conversation — your stylist looking at what your hair is actually doing, not just what you asked for on the booking form.</p><p>For color, we strand-test before we commit. Ammonia-free options are available for every service. And we price by time and product, not by gender — the same cut costs the same, whoever's in the chair.</p>",
            "size": "base",
            "uppercase": false,
            "muted": false
          }
        },
        "philosophy-button": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "link": {
              "text": "How a first visit works",
              "href": "new-clients.html",
              "target": "_self"
            },
            "style": "secondary",
            "size": "medium"
          }
        }
      },
      "blocksOrder": ["philosophy-eyebrow", "philosophy-heading", "philosophy-body", "philosophy-button"]
